swung too slowly. And, a few minutes later, completing
the performance to his own satisfaction,
he struck Hallett out with a neat little drop.        I
preen myself,        said he,        that I       m still there with
82
the huckleberries. As a pitcher of class, I       ve got
Matty and a few others backed up against the
